Package com.commander4j.db

Class JDBQMDictionary

java.lang.Object
com.commander4j.db.JDBQMDictionary
public class JDBQMDictionary extends Object
The JDBQMDictionary class is used to insert/update/delete records from the APP_QM_DICTIONARY table. This table is part of the Quality Module and defines the data required to be captured by the user in the Sample Results Screen.
